    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Vizita la Templul Abu Simbel cu masina privata ,este inclusa masa  ghidul si biletul de intrare.
        Plecarea din Hurghada se face dimineata in jurul orei 5:00  si o sa ajungem in jurul orei 13 :30 ,vizitam templul Fiela si obelisc incomplet dupa care o sa mergem la masa (masa nu este inclusa),dupa care  se poate face Optional insula plantelor unde exista aproape 2000 de specii de plante si copaci din toata lumea si  este cea mai mare insula de pe fuviul Nil si mergem cu barca la satul Nubitilor unde o sa vedeti viata lor si cum cresc crocodili .De pe  barca o sa vedeti un peisaj unic ,piatra de Nil ,nisip si verdeata.Aceasta calatorie dureaza in jur de 1 ora dupa care ne intoarcem la hotel si la ora 4 dimineata plecam la templul Abusibel dupa care nu intoarcem in Hurghada.<br><br>
        Pret:<br>
        depinde de numarul de persoane<br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        intreaba ghidul
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        Visit to Abu Simbel Temple by private car, guide meal and entrance ticket included.
        Departure from Hurghada is done in the morning around 5:00 and we will arrive around 13:30, visit the Fiela temple and incomplete obelisk after which we will go to dinner (meal is not included), after which you can do Optional island plants where there are almost 2000 species of plants and trees from around the world and is the largest island on the Nile River and we go by boat to the village of Nubitilor where you will see their lives and how crocodiles grow. From the boat you will see a unique landscape, Nile stone, sand and greenery. This journey takes about 1 hour after which we return to the hotel and at 4 o'clock in the morning we leave for the temple of Abusibel after which we do not return to Hurghada.
        <br><br>
        Price:<br>
        depends on the number of people.
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        asks the guide
    </p>
